We are a leading developer of school apps in Australia and internationally, providing your parents, staff and students with instant access to real-time information and correspondence through a parent communication app.

We start by getting an understanding of your school’s communication goals in order to build your perfect school app. With a range of flexible modules, we ensure that your parent communication app offers all of the features that are important to your school. We know that every school is different, so we create your school app based purely on your school’s needs.

Parent communication apps are a great way to communicate information quickly and easily. With your eduAPP, you’ll have the ability to quickly and easily manage your eduAPP’s content and communications through a simple content management system. We provide your school with the training you need for our user-friendly system.

With the ability to integrate with leading school systems and programs, we can ensure that your eduAPP is connected with your existing communications. We know that K-12 schools need a range of software systems to operate, so we create customised connections between our school apps and the systems that are important to your school.

We’ve built a range of school app modules to help schools reach their communication and engagement goals. Include only the modules that your school needs and select from a broad range designed to cover all of the key aspects of an effective parent communication app.

Start with our range of standard eduAPP modules for effective communication with your school community. Offer a powerful parent communication app with modules that are designed to keep your school connected and informed.

Add to your suite of standard modules and enhance your school’s eduAPP with premium modules for specialised communication. Take your parent communication app to the next level with our unique range of premium modules.

We are committed to helping schools reach their communication goals, so ask us about custom module development. Every school is unique, as are their needs, so tell us about your objectives and let us customise a module for your school.

With a strong focus on development and growth, we are constantly improving and refining our products. Digistorm eduAPP customers will have access to ongoing  future changes to app modules that are available in regular updates.
We’ve developed school app solutions for a range of schools across Australia, New Zealand and Asia. Here’s what some of our schools think of their customised eduAPP school app solution.

Manage the content on your eduAPP using a simple system on your desktop or mobile. Every eduAPP is managed through a user-friendly content management system, meaning that updates to your parent communication app are quick and easy. You’ll also be able to view reports, make updates or send push notifications quickly and simply through your content management system.

Data on the downloads and use of your school app are important. Using the Digistorm eduAPP content management system, you can understand your community's engagement with your school app. View downloads by device and receive direct feedback from your community for a clear and holistic view of your school app’s success.

Through your content management system, you can add Notices, upload Newsletters, update your Calendar and more. Schools can make updates to the information on their school app without any coding knowledge. Updates are instant and easy to manage, with just a few clicks to send them directly to your school app and to the parent.

The information that your school has to share is important, and can sometimes be urgent. Increase the impact of your update with an instant push notification, sent directly from your content management system. To make sure your message reaches the right members of your school community, you can target your message.

We believe that clever integrations make it easier for our schools to provide their communities with a strong communication solution using their parent communication app. We offer integrations between our eduAPP school app product and leading school systems and programs so that you receive the best possible software solution for your school.

Do you have software systems that are key to your school’s operations? Let us create a mobile extension of your existing platforms with our system specific integrations through our eduAPP school app solution.
Deliver a full customisable eduAPP, designed specifically for Schoolbox to your community.
Access the most important features of your TASS system through a customisable mobile app.
Offer your school community the key aspects of their Edumate system through customised eduAPP modules.

Over the years, our school apps in Australia have continued to be developed and improved, now serving K-12 schools internationally.
Learn more about our story.

Capture, monitor and nurture every prospective enrolment through a Customer Relationship Manager for K-12 schools. Change the way you manage relationships with a school CRM.

Every school is unique, as are the steps that prospective parents pass through during enrolment. Using Funnel, you can create custom enrolment stages through which each potential applicant will pass, based on your school's existing enrolment process.

You'll have a clear view of which enrolment stage each student has reached based on the enrolment steps they’ve taken. Having a view of each student’s enrolment stage allows your school to make more accurate predictions around enrolment numbers.

Our clever system integrations allow your school to reduce admin and improve functionality. Digistorm can connect Funnel with our ENROL online enrolment system as well as a range of online forms for the seamless and simple transfer of data.

The Funnel school CRM interface is user-friendly and offers a comprehensive summary of updates related to prospective enrolments. Get a quick and simple overview of enrolment activity, collect crucial information and manage activity to ensure that the school's relationship with every prospective parent is nurtured.

Your Funnel dashboard gives your school a quick and simple overview of your school CRM activity. View the number of enrolments in each stage of the pipeline, in addition to the number of enrolments over time, pending tasks and latest activity within the system.

Leads are students with the potential to enrol in your school, who have expressed their interest. Instantly view and filter leads and create customised views, segments and lists of potential enrolments. Use the information to forecast enrolment numbers more accurately.

Your Funnel timeline gives you a quick, simple and holistic view of each individual lead. With a clear and comprehensive timeline view, see every interaction, activity and internal task attached to a prospective enrolment with just a single click.
Schools can filter the data of prospective enrolments based on any attribute, in order to access the data they need.

From year of enrolment to enrolment stage and even a combination of multiple filters, schools can filter, save and export any segment they need using Funnel. Improve and increase your online enrolments by accessing specific information and using it to contact and nurture relationships with your school’s important leads.
Your school can analyse crucial data and track enrolments wtih the Reports module.

The visual analytics displays high-volume data by breaking down lead activity and conversion rates at each stage of the enrolment process. Analyse team productivity, your enrolment pipeline and understand where you’re losing your enrolments.

Check your school’s enrolments each month, make year on year comparisons and review geographic data of each applicant. Reports give you complete transparency into the progress of your school’s enrolment process from start to finish.
Easily build and share custom dashboards with your team members. Display a collection of the reports that are most relevant to you.
Funnel offers an Events module that allows parents to book their school tour or open day attendance through a simple, integrated online form.
Build custom forms based on your Open Day or Tour requirements, and offer parents a simple and user-friendly form to collect the data your school needs.
Send reminder emails, check attendees in to their Tours or Open Days and follow up with targeted communication to maximise the ROI of your enrolment events.
Review your conversion rates, view the attendance of existing leads as opposed to new leads and understand the your best performing sources of event registration.

Leveraging years of mobile application development experience, Digistorm has created a dedicated iOS and Android mobile application to ensure that the registration process at your Tour or Open Day is seamless and pain-free. Understand and monitor attendees so that you can tailor post-event communications to them and continue to nurture the prospective parent relationship and encourage an enrolment.
Select specific Leads in the system or select Segments or Lists and send targeted emails to them, directly from Funnel.

Parent communication becomes simple with Funnel. Simply select your relevant list, compose your targeted message and hit send. Got an Open Day coming up? Create a list of next year’s prospective enrolments and send them a reminder to register for the event.
You can select the Leads you'd like to email, or select an entire Segment or List to send to.
Create your email including a custom subject line, content and a call to action button.
Communicate with your selected Leads, all at once. Send immediately or schedule your send.
View a report to understand your email's clicks, opens and deliverability.

What better way to get to know us than to learn our life story? Keep scrolling to find out how we grew from three guys and a bright idea to an industry leader in education technology with 15+ employees.
Digistorm was founded back in 2011 in Burleigh Heads on the sunny Gold Coast. It all started with one director, two employees, a few computers and some big ideas for the education space.
We went on to launch the first school iPhone app for an Australian school. With a skilled developer, a talented creative and an enthusiastic salesperson, we quickly started to grow.
Seeing a need for better communication with the wider community, we began developing school websites. Our expertise allowed us to deliver a high quality solution.
Based on feedback from our clients, we learned that the traditional enrolment landscape was changing. This encouraged us to build our comprehensive online enrolment system.
With a growing team, client base and product scope, we realised it was time to improve our support offering. We now have a dedicated Support Team, Support Centre and Support App.
Recognising a gap in the industry, we built and released a comprehensive Customer Relationship Management product to manage enrolments in K-12 schools.
Our passion is for staying ahead of the curve, so we’re constantly striving to reach a new frontier in education technology. Continue to follow our journey here.
We're confident in our delivery of powerful and intelligent systems for smarter schools. Here’s how we do it.
We help schools reach their goals by building our systems based on each school’s individual requirements.
Our range of system integrations allows us to deliver seamless software solutions for schools.
Software must continue evolving to stay competitive, so we roll out regular improvements to our clients.
Ongoing research about shifts and changes within education technology allows us to be industry leaders.
Digistorm is proudly Australian, with a Gold Coast-based team servicing clients across Australasia.
We work hard to provide support to Digistorm clients in a range of ways, specific to their product.

At Digistorm, we understand that you need a range of powerful K-12 school software to reach all of your school’s objectives.

That’s why we’ve worked with some leading school software providers to create clever connections with our range of products. Learn more about our range of product integrations, or get in touch to discuss a new one.

Our range of product offers a very specific range of benefits to K-12 schools. Here’s how each Digistorm product, from our parent communication app to our school websites can connect with leading K-12 school systems as well as smaller systems that enhance the Digistorm product.

The eduAPP parent communication app is a powerful way to keep parents informed and to distribute important information. Product integrations with the eduAPP school app allow schools to enhance the features of, and the way in which their eduAPP is used.
Our custom integration between the eduAPP and the Schoolbox system allows Schoolbox schools to access the modules that are important to them from a customised and clever school app.

We’ve worked with TASS as their first certified API developers to create the TASS Parent Module within the Digistorm eduAPP. TASS schools can offer parents the features that they need within a customised school app product.
The eduAPP for Edumate offers every important Edumate feature within the eduAPP school app product, in addition to the modules designed by Digistorm.

Edsmart schools can now offer their form products to students and parents through the Digistorm eduAPP product. This custom integration offers key Edsmart features in addition to important school app modules.

We’ve worked with leading School Management Systems to create custom connections with ENROL. Once you’ve collected online enrolments through the ENROL system, our integrations will allow you to transfer data quickly and easily to your school’s system.

One of the key benefits of the ENROL online enrolment system is your school’s ability to collect enrolment or application fees online. Schools can quickly and easily collect payments using the Stripe solution or our integrations with major banks.

There are a number of ways in which we can integrate your school’s responsive, customised school website with other software systems. From form data moving seamlessly to your CRM system to the implementation of various plug-ins and more, Digistorm’s eduSITE product is flexible and capable of clever product integrations.

Digistorm’s customer relationship management tool, Funnel continues to be developed, focusing on nurturing relationships with prospective parents. Ensure that all of the data you capture on your school website or other forms enters your Funnel CRM seamlessly with custom product integrations offered by Digistorm.

Some of our system integrations offer benefits to your school that improve and increase productivity using simple connections. Our range of integrations with common organisational, marketing and social media systems allow schools to enhance Digistorm products and improve their outputs.

Showcase what makes your school unique with a fully responsive school website that is easy to manage and developed to meet your objectives.

Every school is different, so we’ll tailor your school website features to the communication and information needs of your school community. We’re committed to providing customised solutions to assist K-12 schools in reaching their online goals, using strategically built, professionally designed, responsive and effective school websites.

Manage every aspect of your school website with a content management system (CMS) that is easy to use and requires no programming knowledge. Our preferred CMS is Craft, because it simplifies the uploading, changing and updating of content on your school website. Minimise the time and effort your school spends on website content updates.

Your school website will be built using the latest UI, UX, SEO and web standards. Our experienced team of school website developers will ensure that your functionality requirements are fulfilled. Our team has not only technical skills, but years of experience in the K-12 school industry. School websites are what we do best!

Your eduSITE is built on a simple content management system which allows you to quickly and easily make changes to your school website, even with no programming knowledge. Your team will be trained so that you know how to manage every aspect.

Connect your Google Analytics account and view key statistics about your school website's performance on your dashboard. We understand how important it is to monitor the performance of your eduSITE, so we make website reporting simple for your school.

Quickly and easily add new pages and blog or news posts to your school's website, with no coding knowledge needed. Our focus is on ensuring that you don’t need to engage developers to make changes or additions to your eduSITE, so we make it super simple.

Build your pages using a range of custom modules such as image galleries, quotes, text blocks, call to action buttons, forms and more. You’ll be able to continue to customise your school website pages by simply dragging and dropping custom modules on each page.
Once launched, you’ll receive comprehensive training so that you understand how to easily update your school website. You’ll also receive documentation and have ongoing access to our
Help Centre
, where you can view a range of school website documentation or log a support ticket for assistance from our team. The Digistorm team will be here to support you throughout the life of your eduSITE.
With over 70 school websites designed and built, you don’t have to take our word for it. Hear eduSITE reviews from some of the best schools in Australia, New Zealand and internationally.

We have a team of designers and developers who have the knowledge and experience to build your school website based on best practise principles. Based on your school’s needs and objectives, we take care of every aspect of your eduSITE design and development so that you can focus on your content.
Your school’s website will optimise the user experience across multiple platforms and devices, with automatic reconfiguration for an effective website on every screen.
User interface and user experience are key pillars for the design and structure of every Digistorm school website, so we’ll ensure your eduSITE is user friendly.
Essential aspects of your school website will be composed based on SEO best practise, to ensure that your website is favoured by leading search engines.
Your eduSITE will be compatible across multiple browsers and devices, and will always render correctly. You can rest assured your school website will have great usability.

We use load balanced networks to ensure that eduSITE traffic is managed, ensuring fast page load speeds across all of our websites. All Digistorm eduSITEs are encrypted with an SSL certificate as standard, meaning that information passed through your school website is protected.
Digistorm uses industry-leading Amazon Web Hosting for all eduSITEs, meaning that your website and its’ data are secure, compliant and have an industry leading uptime of 99.95%.

Guide prospective families through a seamless online enrolment portal and streamline your internal admissions process with an online enrolment management system.

Our designers and developers create a custom online enrolment form that represents your school and easily collects the information that you need. Your school’s online enrolment form will be responsive, user-friendly and will connect directly with your online enrolment management system.

Understand your enrolment pipeline by using ENROL’s online enrolment management system. Make the most of your school’s online enrolments by viewing, reviewing, updating and exporting applications for easy import into your SMS. ENROL makes online enrolments simple for K-12 schools.

We can add a payment gateway to your online application form and integrate with leading banks so that your school can collect application fees during enrolment. With the ENROL online enrolment system, key enrolment functions are made simple for both the parent, and for the school.

ENROL’s online enrolment form for parents makes it easy for parents to complete, change and pay for their child’s enrolment. Parents can commence their online enrolment and finish it at a time that suits them, from the comfort of their own home, or even on the go from their mobile. Reminders are sent to ensure that parents complete their paused online enrolments.

Parents are welcomed by a branded landing page with important information about the school’s online enrolment process. The landing page serves as an instructional tool that starts the parent’s online enrolment using the ENROL form.

Your customised form guides parents through simple steps that provide you with the information your school needs. The form is mobile-responsive, user-friendly and the form’s fields collect the information your school needs.

If your school needs to collect documents or files during the online enrolment process, they can be added simply through ENROL. Parents can upload documents required for their enrolment quickly and easily from their computer or mobile.

Emails are an effective way to communicate with applicants throughout the online enrolment process. Welcome, reminder and confirmation emails support the parent’s journey through their online enrolment form.

Every part of the online enrolment process is taken care of by the ENROL online enrolment management system. Parents can complete the payment for their enrolment online using a safe and secure payment gateway.
Our bespoke online enrolment solutions have changed the way that over 50 schools manage their enrolments.

You can view your enrolments at any time within the ENROL online enrolment system. Reduce your paper trail with key enrolment information being collected and held online in a simple and effective interface. Manual data entry becomes a thing of the past, with information entered into online enrolment forms entering the ENROL system automatically. View an applicants progress through their online enrolment, communicate with applicants and change the status of their online enrolment. Once completed, export online enrolment applications and upload them directly to your school management system.

At Digistorm, we know how valuable your enrolment information is. Using the ENROL online enrolment solution, you’ll understand the suburbs your enrolments are coming from, which stage of the process applicants have reached and where your form traffic is coming from.

Connect the ENROL system with your internal processes by downloading or exporting applications. Once you’ve exported your online enrolment applications, you can save them or upload them directly to your school’s SMS, creating a simple internal process.
We believe in making your school’s enrolment process as smooth as possible, so we’re able to integrate with key financial institutions and provide you with an online payment gateway.
Enrol has modernised and simplified our Enrolment process significantly.

The application process for both Boarding and International students who do not live locally is now far more user-friendly and proficient. And, Digistorm support are always friendly, willing and able to assist when required!

The Digistorm team were very helpful in the set-up stages, and have always been quick to respond to our requests to change or streamline the online process to suit our needs. Collection of data has improved, and the ease of an online form has encouraged families to make earlier application.

Not only have we reduced administration time, we now also work within a system that holds all of our enrolment information in one place. It's been really helpful collecting enrolment fees through the system, too.
